{"tid":422460,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[樂隊招人] 原創poprock, 廣東話, 招鼓手","createTime":"2017-10-03T05:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T14:11:52.000Z","uid":105976,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e03486e7bcd1fbb95cf47a44986b281c3fb9a97","tid":422460,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"誠招 鼓手 男女不拘, <br />\n<br />\n因為係原創歌 大家要寫返自已果段入去 (暫時用guitar pro寫譜) , 我作主旋律 之後盡量加左其他樂器俾你地參考,  有晒base chord, 自已度下改下<br />\n鼓果部份我通常有好基本既 你都自已諗下<br />\n<br />\n長期有熱誠 有責任感 可以創作到你既部份 之後打返譜 (幾多野要做)<br />\n(暫時有2首 高度完成度原創歌) 有幾首整緊 岩既會長夾,<br />\n<br />\n夾既地方有觀塘 tko 北角 旺角<br />\n<br />\n現有vocal ,keyboard手, 電結他&amp; 結他手  bass, 成員2x歲up<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曲風 類似 mr children, 生物股長 <br />\n重視旋律 <br />\n<br />\n** 我地唔係玩heavy or metal野 , 鐘意呢類既話 一定唔岩你**<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以加telegram group傾 聽下曲風岩唔岩你 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/ErVDahAaL3DmG-7kLLhCzg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FErVDahAaL3DmG-7kLLhCzg&d=hSaw7YAqDoR7w%2BFi8M%2Fsyr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=aa4fc4ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/ErVDahAaL3DmG-7kLLhCzg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n**呢個ac問朋友借"},{"pid":"3901358f85bd33b23463462c49d8e7557c23b9b4","tid":422460,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbaf8f087215604dacd2947f5cce3e61b67dc3f","tid":422460,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ceda86a71c31503aaf1e030f3bfa3a742a0b18c","tid":422460,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886d5cf69c3c3375ffc5f5999a301a09ddaed172","tid":42246